#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:1
msgid "Asset Storage"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:3
msgid ""
"From v1.3.0, BPMN processes, form schemas, and document templates are "
"persisted to PostgreSQL via the LDE backend. The frontend uses a **write-"
"through cache with async hydration**: all reads are synchronous from "
"`localStorage` (zero-latency UI), writes update `localStorage` immediately "
"and then POST to the backend in the background, and on editor mount a `GET` "
"hydration call replaces local non-readonly records with the authoritative "
"server state."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:7
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:8
msgid ""
"graph TD\n"
"    A[Editor component] -->|mount| B[hydrateFromServer]\n"
"    A -->|save| C[localStorage cache]\n"
"    B -->|background fetch| D[LDE Backend]\n"
"    D --> E[(PostgreSQL — lde_assets)]"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:18
msgid "Write-through cache strategy"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:20
msgid "On **save**, each service:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:22
msgid ""
"Writes the updated record to `localStorage` immediately — the UI reflects "
"the change synchronously with zero latency."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:23
msgid ""
"Fires a background `fetch` to `POST /v1/assets/{type}` — no `await`, no "
"spinner. If the network call fails, a warning is logged to the browser "
"console but the user experience is unaffected."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:25
msgid "On **delete**, each service:"
msgstr ""

